OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1782197284
OL,3,CChanges to bin collection times as 40C
OL,4,Cheatwave to hit UK
OL,6,FSome bin collection times are changing
OL,7,Fthis week as parts of England and
OL,8,FWales brace for a heatwave that could
OL,9,Fsee temperatures of up to 40C.
OL,11,FMultiple councils have announced they
OL,12,Fwill start collection rounds as early
OL,13,Fas 5am to help their teams cope in the
OL,14,Fextreme temperatures after the Met
OL,15,FOffice issued a red warning for
OL,16,FWednesday and Thursday this week.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/6
