OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1782197284
OL,3,CChanges to bin collection times as 40C
OL,4,Cheatwave to hit UK
OL,6,FThe forecast stretches between
OL,7,FBirmingham, Salisbury, Swansea and
OL,8,FLondon, with a wider amber warning
OL,9,Falso in place for most of southern
OL,10,FEngland and Wales, reaching up to
OL,11,FBangor, Preston, Leeds and Liverpool
OL,12,Ffor Wednesday and Thursday.
OL,14,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,15,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,16,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,17,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
