FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1782197284
OL,3,CChanges to bin collection times as 40C
OL,4,Cheatwave to hit UK
OL,6,FCollection rounds will begin from 5am
OL,7,Fin Bristol, 5.30am in South
OL,8,FGloucestershire, while Cheltenham
OL,9,FBorough Council, Somerset Council,
OL,10,FShropshire Council and Tendering
OL,11,FCouncil have said workers will start
OL,12,Fat 6am.
OL,14,FCollections will also begin from
OL,15,Faround 6.20am to 6.30am in Central
OL,16,FBedfordshire, the council said.
OL,18,FResidents have been advised to put
OL,19,Ftheir bins out the night before so
OL,20,Fthey don't miss the new times.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1782197284
OL,3,CChanges to bin collection times as 40C
OL,4,Cheatwave to hit UK
OL,6,F"This is to help our crews and
OL,7,Fvehicles cope in the heat and ensure
OL,8,Fthat they're able to complete the
OL,9,Fscheduled collections," said
OL,10,FCouncillor Steve Harvey said of the
OL,11,Fchanges in Cheltenham.
OL,13,F"Residents are asked to put their
OL,14,Frecycling boxes, food caddies, refuse
OL,15,Fand garden bins out for collection at
OL,16,Fkerbside by 6am.
OL,18,F"Our crews will do their very best to
OL,19,Fbe as quiet as possible whilst out
OL,20,Fcollecting earlier in the morning."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/6
