OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1782197284
OL,3,CChanges to bin collection times as 40C
OL,4,Cheatwave to hit UK
OL,6,FThe Met Office has warned that the
OL,7,Fincoming heatwave carries a risk to
OL,8,Flife for everyone and is likely to
OL,9,Fcause significant disruption to travel.
OL,11,FEnergy supplies, such as water,
OL,12,Felectricity, gas or mobile phone
OL,13,Fservices, could also be impacted and
OL,14,Fpeople should take care when heading
OL,15,Fto beaches or lakes due to the chances
OL,16,Fof cold water shock.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/6
