OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1782197284
OL,3,CChanges to bin collection times as 40C
OL,4,Cheatwave to hit UK
OL,6,FThe Met Office strongly recommends
OL,7,Fkeeping out of the sun, drinking
OL,8,Fplenty of fluids and avoiding
OL,9,Fexercising between 11am and 3pm when
OL,10,Fthe sun is the strongest.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/6
